(217, 48, 'left_content_ul_2', '<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complimentary Roof Inspections</strong>: To start our work together, a roof repair specialist will assess your property, identify any damaged areas, and come up with a plan to make things right. We’ll also provide a complimentary inspection and roof repair estimate.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Trained &amp; Certified Professionals</strong>: Our team is comprised of Owens Corning Preferred Contractors, CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicators, and GAF-certified experts. That means you can expect the highest quality of care for your home.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Protective Warranties</strong>: Our roof repair contractors back our work with 100% workmanship coverage in addition to Owens Corning warranties. That way, you can have the ultimate peace of mind for years to come.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(218, 48, '_left_content_ul_2', 'field_630db45b3f61c'),
