(477, 73, 'left_content_3', 'An older roof can develop a water leak at any moment. You might want to consider a new roof replacement before problems occur. If you want to meet with <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\">our roof contractors</a> to discuss your options, consider calling us to set up an appointment and a complimentary roof inspection.\r\n\r\nYou can also ask us about:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">Storm Damage Restoration</a>​</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOne of our contractors can provide a roof replacement estimate during your consultation. If needed, we can also help you through the insurance claims process for a storm-damaged roof. Contact us today!'),
