(597, 100, 'left_content_1', 'A storm has hit your neighborhood and done a lot of damage to your roof. There\'s a possibility that you will need to file an insurance claim to get the repairs completed. At Bartlett Roofing, we’ve worked with a good many homeowners to get their properties restored to better-than-before condition. In fact, our team has also worked with insurance companies on covered restorations. Not every project is exactly the same, but here is a quick look at what usually happens when you contact Bartlett Roofing.'),
