(605, 100, 'left_content_3', 'If you are ready to get a roof inspection completed by Bartlett Roofing, give us a call or fill out our online form. We offer services in the areas of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\">Residential Roofing</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Damage Restoration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur contractors can provide a complimentary inspection for your roof repairs. We can also go over our flexible financing plans and warranty protection during your appointment.'),
