(663, 102, 'left_content_1', 'Bartlett Roofing started out as a family-owned framing crew back in the early 90s. Today, owner Doug Bartlett has transformed the business into a full-service roofing and restoration business that services multiple states throughout the country, including Idaho, Montana, Nevada, Oregon, Utah, Washington, and Wyoming. Our top-rated services now include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Solutions</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Damage Restoration Care</li>\r\n</ul>'),
