(667, 102, 'left_content_2', 'Doug Bartlett learned everything he knows about the exterior remodeling industry from his dad and uncle. Through the years, Doug has built the Bartlett Roofing team from the ground up, training and educating them in the Bartlett Method.\r\n\r\nThe staple of the Bartlett Method is to provide comprehensive care that meets our customers’ unique wants and needs. When the project is over, we want to be able to ask our clients if they are 100% satisfied and have them come back with a guaranteed “yes!”'),
