(809, 116, 'left_content_1', 'At Bartlett Roofing, we’re known for many things—but quality is certainly at the top of the list! That’s why we’re proud to be an <strong>Owens Corning Preferred Contractor</strong>. As a top roofing manufacturer nationwide, this trusted brand shares our rigorous standards of excellence and our commitment to long-term warranty protection.'),
