(885, 118, 'left_content_2', 'Asphalt roofing shingles are one of the most popular options for residential roof systems, especially when the installation is done by a professional roofing company. At Bartlett Roofing, we offer the best asphalt roof options for all types of homes. There are many reasons why you should choose an asphalt roof system for your home. For starters, asphalt systems are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Versatile</strong>: Asphalt shingles can cover all types of roof systems, regardless of size, shape, or roofline. Plus, we offer a wide range of designs, colors, and styles, so you can enhance your home’s curb appeal according to your personal aesthetic.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Cost-Effective</strong>: Asphalt roof shingles are one of the most affordable roofing options on the market. Not only are they cheaper to install, but they also last long enough to provide great value.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durable</strong>: Our roof shingles can withstand high winds, storms, and even fire in some cases. They’re also algae-resistant, so you don’t have to struggle with time-consuming maintenance.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low-Maintenance</strong>: An asphalt roof replacement with our roofing company is simple and stress-free. These shingles are easy to install, <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/repair/\">repair</a>, and maintain over time, which means you can enjoy the benefits of a quality roof system without a lot of hard work.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
