(983, 122, 'left_content_1', 'Bartlett Roofing offers quality tile roof replacement for customers across the Upper Midwest. Our team can make sure your tile roof is attractive, stylish, and properly installed. We also boast excellent workmanship warranties that protect your new roof for up to 5 years.\r\n\r\nAllow our roofing company to replace broken tiles or install a replacement tile roof for your property. We will make sure you get beautiful results without having to break your budget thanks to flexible financing and inclusive estimates.'),
(984, 122, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dae8178fa3'),
(985, 122, 'left_content_header_2', 'The Unique Beauty and Longevity of a Tile Roof'),
(986, 122, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(987, 122, 'left_content_2', 'If you are looking for a material that befits the local climate and provides decades of protection, tiles are it. Tile roofing brings a sense of style and elegance to homes across the Southwest. Bartlett Roofing can install different tile roof types — everything from a classic Mission style to more modern shingles. Whether you are looking for traditional clay or concrete roof tiles, our team has the experience needed to <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement/\">replace your roof</a>.\r\n\r\nTile roofs also bring plenty of benefits for the homeowner, like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Excellent Weather Resistance</strong>: The extreme durability of clay and concrete means it easily outlasts rain, wind, and baking sunshine.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low-Maintenance</strong>: Tile is also a fairly resistant product, so it doesn’t require as much maintenance as other materials.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Long Lifespan</strong>: As a product that doesn’t rot or invite insects, tile can last from several decades up to a century in some regions of the country.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(988, 122, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(989, 122, 'left_content_header_3', 'Sign up for a Complimentary Inspection on Our Roofing Services'),
(990, 122, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
