(1039, 124, 'left_content_2', 'When it comes to planning a roof installation, it’s important to choose a material that meets all your style and performance needs. That’s why the experts at Bartlett Roofing offer the best slate roofing options for homes of all shapes and sizes.\r\n\r\nWe offer the highest-quality products from <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\">Owens Corning</a>, CertainTeed, GAF, and more, so you can choose the best options for your home. As your trusted local slate roofers, you can count on us to provide the best options in terms of:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendliness</strong>: Slate can be recycled, which means it won’t negatively impact the environment when it comes time to replace it.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durability</strong>: Although slate roof systems are more expensive upfront, they can last up to 150 years or longer. Plus, they don’t require much maintenance, making them a great choice for any home.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Resistance</strong>: Slate is a great material for your roof system because it is fireproof, resistant to mold and fungus, and can’t be penetrated by water either. Whatever the world throws at you, you can count on your slate roof to stand strong.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Beauty</strong>: To top it off, slate roofs look amazing. No matter the style of your home, a slate roof contributes to a rustic aesthetic that is also timeless and elegant.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
