(1238, 146, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_630dbc2c9a09e'),
(1239, 146, 'left_content_1', 'Your commercial property is one of your most important investments, so when it’s time for a new roof, be sure that you choose a roofing company that delivers flawless results using premium asphalt roof replacement materials. By doing exactly that, the Bartlett Roofing team has built a solid reputation for excellence one job at a time.\r\n\r\nOur commitment to quality has earned us a long-standing A+ rating with the BBB, many positive customer reviews, and our place as the trusted choice for commercial roofing replacements and repairs.\r\n\r\nNo project is too big or too small, and we work to complete projects quickly to minimize disruption to your business’ normal routine.'),
(1240, 146, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(1241, 146, 'left_content_header_2', 'Premium Materials and Expert Installation'),
(1242, 146, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(1243, 146, 'left_content_2', 'Bartlett Roofing has experience working on <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing</a> projects of every size. Whether you need a simple repair for your asphalt roof or a new roofing system, our roofing company offers impressive benefits that make us the smart choice.\r\n\r\nWe provide:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Premium Materials:</strong> Bartlett Roofing is an elite contractor for top roofing brands, including GAF, Owens Corning, and CertainTeed.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Expert Workmanship:</strong> Every roofer on our team has the skills and experience to provide exceptional results for your <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">commercial roofing repair</a> or installation project.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Competitive Prices:</strong> We do what we can to keep our prices competitive without sacrificing quality. We also offer attractive financing options that make it easier to budget for your roofing project.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Industry-Leading Warranties:</strong> You’ll have peace of mind knowing that your new commercial asphalt roof is covered by one of the best warranties in the business.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe also provide <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">comprehensive storm damage restoration services</a>.'),
(1244, 146, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(1245, 146, 'left_content_header_3', 'Schedule a Complimentary Inspection with Our Highly Skilled Commercial Roofing Professionals'),
