(1281, 148, 'left_content_1', 'Are you in need of a new roof system for your business? You’ve come to the right place. For more than 25 years, the Bartlett Roofing team has been perfecting their process for designing and installing high-quality metal roofs for all types of businesses. As a GAF-certified and BBB-accredited roofing company, we know what it takes to design the perfect roof system for every customer.'),
(1282, 148, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(1283, 148, 'left_content_header_2', 'Top-Rated Metal Roof Options for Your Property'),
(1284, 148, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(1285, 148, 'left_content_2', 'When it comes to choosing the right roof system for your property, you have to consider all your wants and needs for your space. Fortunately, our metal roofers are here to help you through the process. There are many options from which you can choose for your property. For starters, check out the top benefits of our metal roofs:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Long Lifespan</strong>: Metal is highly sustainable and can last three times as long as asphalt shingles without requiring much maintenance.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendly Materials</strong>: Metal roof systems are 100% recyclable, which means they won’t impact the environment when they finally need replacing.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy-Efficient Capabilities</strong>: Our metal roofs are designed to lower your energy bills. This is because they are made with reflective coatings with integrated thermal breaks.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Stylish Options</strong>: Our experts offer a wide range of metal roof options that are designed to match any aesthetic. Whether you want the modern look of metal or a more traditional style, we’ve got you covered.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Weather Resistance</strong>: Metal roof systems are made with panels that interlock, providing premium wind resistance when compared to other roofing options.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Fire Resistance</strong>: Metal is extremely resistant to fire, which will help keep your property safer in the case of an emergency.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1286, 148, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(1287, 148, 'left_content_header_3', 'Get Started with a Complimentary Inspection from Our Commercial Roofers'),
(1288, 148, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_63192f9e025f1'),
(1289, 148, 'left_content_3', 'As your <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing\">trusted commercial roofers</a>, Bartlett Roofing knows what it takes to provide the highest-quality roof systems for properties of all shapes and sizes. Plus, our metal roofing installers offer flexible financing options, protective warranties, and unmatched customer care. To satisfy the needs of all our unique customers, we offer a wide range of commercial roofing services, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Multi-Family Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/replacement/\">Roof Replacements</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGive us a call to learn more about our services or fill out our online form to receive a complimentary inspection from our metal roofing company today.'),
