(1392, 159, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_630dae5d78fa2'),
(1393, 159, 'left_content_1', 'When you require roof replacement, choose a company with plenty of experience and in-depth training. With 25+ years of experience under our belts, the contractors at Bartlett Roofing are the team for the job. We’ve spent many years in the home remodeling industry honing our skills as contractors.\r\n\r\nOur experienced roofing company will put the focus on your needs as the property owner. We complete a thorough 40-point inspection of every roof before even offering an estimate. Our team will also make time to meet with you to discuss roofing shingle options, materials, and colors. Better yet, customers will enjoy the services of an ethical business with BBB accreditation and A+ rating. We make it a point to create a positive experience, so you’ll love the work we do — and your roof — for a lifetime.'),
(1394, 159, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dae8178fa3'),
(1395, 159, 'left_content_header_2', 'Quality Roofing Replacement Services by Trained Experts'),
(1396, 159, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(1397, 159, 'left_content_2', 'Of course, your new roof is only as good as the contractors who install it. That’s why Bartlett Roofing strives to maintain multiple brand certifications, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\">Owens Corning Preferred Contractor</a>​</li>\r\n 	<li>CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF Certified</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are factory trained to provide complete roof replacement using these top-quality brands. Additionally, our contractors are experienced with a variety of other products and materials, like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/metal/\">Metal Roofing</a>​</li>\r\n 	<li>Wood Shake Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Slate Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Flat Roofing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAs one of the premier roof replacement companies across multiple states, we also protect your investment with a 100% workmanship warranty for 5 years. Whether you have a home or a business that needs a new roof, this warranty will ensure you have a little extra peace of mind.\r\n\r\nAs one of the premier roof replacement companies across multiple states, we also protect your investment with a 100% workmanship warranty for 5 years. Whether you have a home or a business that needs a new roof, this warranty will ensure you have a little extra peace of mind.'),
(1398, 159, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(1399, 159, 'left_content_header_3', 'Ask About a Complimentary Inspection and Estimate for a Replacement Roof'),
(1400, 159, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
(1401, 159, 'left_content_3', 'An older roof can develop a water leak at any moment. You might want to consider a new roof replacement before problems occur. If you want to meet with <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\">our roof contractors</a> to discuss your options, consider calling us to set up an appointment and a complimentary roof inspection.\r\n\r\nYou can also ask us about:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">Storm Damage Restoration</a>​</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOne of our contractors can provide a roof replacement estimate during your consultation. If needed, we can also help you through the insurance claims process for a storm-damaged roof. Contact us today!'),
(1402, 159, '_left_content_3', 'field_630daeb578fa8'),
(1403, 159, 'residential_roofing_bread_crumb', 'Roof Replacement'),
(1404, 159, '_residential_roofing_bread_crumb', 'field_630daec878fa9'),
