(1462, 162, 'left_content_1', 'Bartlett Roofing is a professional roofing company, powered by a team with over 25 years of roofing experience. From the time we opened our doors until now, our team has earned an A+ rating and accreditation with the Better Business Bureau as well as certifications from Owens Corning, GAF, and CertainTeed.\r\n\r\nFrom <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">minor repairs</a> to full-scale replacements, we can handle all your roofing needs for your property. Here, we’ll specifically be talking about the latter: custom roof replacements.'),
