(1469, 162, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dbc2ca8ba0'),
(1470, 162, 'left_content_3', 'If you’re ready to learn more about our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing services</a>, get in touch with the local experts at Bartlett Roofing right away. Our team will be by your side through every step of the process to ensure you’re left with a durable roof system that lasts. Plus, we offer a wide range of products and services:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roof Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/multi-family-roofing/\">Multi-Family Roof Care</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Long-Lasting Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Asphalt Shingles</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roof Membranes</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing Options</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGet in touch with our local roofing team today to learn more about our roof replacement services. You can also fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection with our experts.'),
