(1589, 142, 'left_content_1', 'When it comes to multi-family home roofing projects, there’s no better partner to have by your side than Bartlett Roofing. Our professional commercial roofing company has over 25 years of experience designing and installing multi-family roofs for many different buildings.\r\n\r\nOn top of being a BBB-accredited business with an A+ rating, Bartlett Roofing is also GAF-certified, which means you can count on us to provide the best services for all our unique customers. Ready to learn more? Call the best multi-family roofing company near you right away!'),
