(1631, 144, 'left_content_1', 'When it comes to <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/replacement/\">replacing your roof system</a>, there are many options from which you can choose. If you’re considering roof coatings, you’re in the right place. Bartlett Roofing has over 25 years of experience sourcing and installing top-quality roof coatings for properties of all shapes and sizes.\r\n\r\nAlong the way, we have become an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified business, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator. We’re also BBB-accredited with an A+ rating! All this being said, you can count on us to make your commercial roof coating project a breeze.'),
