(1717, 150, 'left_content_1', 'As a business owner, you know how important it is to have a safe and durable property. Part of that means having a quality roof system. At Bartlett Roofing, we know what it takes to design and install the best roofs for all types of businesses, including high-quality TPO roofing.\r\n\r\nAs a BBB-accredited and A+ rated business, we can provide the best products, resources, and services to ensure you get the best fit for your space. Read on to learn more about our TPO roofing options.'),
