(1765, 152, 'left_content_2', 'Having a high-quality roof system for your business will keep your employees and assets safe and secure. At Bartlett Roofing, we offer the best clay and concrete roof tiles that look great and last a lifetime. As a GAF-certified business, you can depend on us to provide the best installation care and customer support.\r\n\r\nSo, why choose a tile roof system anyways? The benefits are endless, but we’ll start here:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>High Resistance</strong>: Tile roof systems are highly resistant to both weather and pests, which means you won’t have to worry about expensive damage over time.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low Maintenance</strong>: Because tile roofs are so durable, they require very little maintenance, saving you time and money on upkeep and repairs.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Impressive Longevity</strong>: Once you install a tile roof system, you can expect to have it for upwards of 50 years!</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: Purposely installed to leave a gap underneath, a tile roofing system will help block the sun’s heat, saving you money on energy bills from season to season.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Customizability</strong>: Our tile roof types come in a wide range of styles and colors, so you can completely customize your building’s exterior.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendliness</strong>: Since tiles are usually made from clay or concrete, they are completely sustainable and easily recyclable to lessen their impact on the environment.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
