(1871, 175, 'left_content_1', 'You may not think that wind can have a devastating impact on your roof system, but it can actually wreak a lot of havoc. Fortunately, you won’t have to deal with the aftermath by yourself. Bartlett Roofing is a professional wind restoration company helping homeowners and businesses with all their restoration needs.\r\n\r\nOver the past 25 years, we have earned an A+ rating with the Better Business Bureau and certification with GAF, too. More importantly, we’ve gained the respect of thousands of customers through our stress-free wind restoration services and unparalleled customer care. Ready to start planning your project? Our roofing company is just a quick call away.'),
(1872, 175, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dfc9190733'),
