(1935, 177, 'left_content_1', 'Did you know that hail as small as a dime can cause damage that requires a roof repair? After a storm comes through, turn to the local roofing company that brings decades of experience providing hail damage repair services.\r\n\r\nBartlett Roofing has helped thousands of homeowners repair hail-damaged roofs, and our fast response time and consistently excellent results make it easy to see why we’re the smart choice. Over the years, we’ve maintained an A+ rating with the BBB and earned many positive reviews from past customers.\r\n\r\nWant to know the best part?\r\n\r\nBecause we have local <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm damage repair professionals</a>, we can respond to your call for service quickly. This allows us to provide temporary measures to prevent secondary damage until repairs are made.'),
(1936, 177, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dfc9190733'),
(1937, 177, 'left_content_header_2', 'Complimentary Hail Damage Roof Repair Inspection'),
(1938, 177, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dfc91941ce'),
(1939, 177, 'left_content_2', 'A lot of homeowners think a visual inspection is enough to rule out roof hail damage, but they are mistaken. The fact is that all damage can’t be seen from the ground, so it’s important to have an inspection completed following any major weather event.\r\n\r\nHere’s why:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>If you overlook damage, you leave your home susceptible to secondary damage from leaking.</li>\r\n 	<li>Such damage likely won\'t be noticed until significant issues have occurred inside your home, such as mold or leaks that penetrate main living areas.</li>\r\n 	<li>The more time that passes, the more difficult it becomes to link damage to a storm. This could result in the denial of what would otherwise have been a covered repair.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBartlett Roofing provides thorough inspections at no cost, and our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\">highly reviewed roofing company</a> provides all the documentation needed to ensure your hail damage roof repair or replacement claim is properly valued.'),
