(3169, 290, 'left_content_1', 'When you require roof replacement, choose a company with plenty of experience and in-depth training. With 25+ years of experience under our belts, the contractors at Bartlett Roofing are the team for the job. We’ve spent many years in the home remodeling industry honing our skills as contractors.\r\n\r\nOur experienced roofing company will put the focus on your needs as the property owner. We complete a thorough 40-point inspection of every roof before even offering an estimate. Our team will also make time to meet with you to discuss roofing shingle options, materials, and colors. Better yet, customers will enjoy the services of an ethical business with BBB accreditation and A+ rating. We make it a point to create a positive experience, so you’ll love the work we do — and your roof — for a lifetime.'),
