(3173, 290, 'left_content_2', 'Of course, your new roof is only as good as the contractors who install it. That’s why Bartlett Roofing strives to maintain multiple brand certifications, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\">Owens Corning Preferred Contractor</a>​</li>\r\n 	<li>CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF Certified</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe are factory trained to provide complete roof replacement using these top-quality brands. Additionally, our contractors are experienced with a variety of other products and materials, like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>​<a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/metal/\">Metal Roofing</a>​</li>\r\n 	<li>Wood Shake Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Slate Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Flat Roofing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAs one of the premier roof replacement companies across multiple states, we also protect your investment with a 100% workmanship warranty for 5 years. Whether you have a home or a business that needs a new roof, this warranty will ensure you have a little extra peace of mind.\r\n\r\nAs one of the premier roof replacement companies across multiple states, we also protect your investment with a 100% workmanship warranty for 5 years. Whether you have a home or a business that needs a new roof, this warranty will ensure you have a little extra peace of mind.'),
