(3247, 291, 'left_content_3', 'As your trusted <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing\">local roofing company</a>, Bartlett Roofing knows how best to keep your home in top shape no matter what the world throws at it. Through our comprehensive repairs and protective warranties, we guarantee you’ll roof system will look and perform at its best for years to come.\r\n\r\nPlus, we offer a variety of other services and products, so you can take care of your roof system regardless of what state it is in. These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Full Roof Replacements</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\">Owens Corning Roof Options</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roof Shingles</li>\r\n 	<li>Wood Shake Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Slate Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Low-Slope Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li><em>… and more!</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAre you ready to start planning your roof repair project? Get in touch with our local roofers to learn more about our offerings or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection now.'),
(3248, 291, '_left_content_3', 'field_630daeb578fa8'),
