(3305, 292, 'left_content_1', 'At Bartlett Roofing, we’re known for many things—but quality is certainly at the top of the list! That’s why we’re proud to be an <strong>Owens Corning Preferred Contractor</strong>. As a top roofing manufacturer nationwide, this trusted brand shares our rigorous standards of excellence and our commitment to long-term warranty protection.'),
(3306, 292, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dae8178fa3'),
(3307, 292, 'left_content_header_2', 'Why Choose an Owens Corning Roof?'),
(3308, 292, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(3309, 292, 'left_content_2', 'There are many benefits to an Owens Corning roof, and our customers ultimately choose this brand for a variety of reasons. No matter which benefit is most compelling to you, you can expect to enjoy every aspect of this award-winning roofing system:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Beauty</strong>: Owens Corning roof shingles come in several different styles, including <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/asphalt/\">architectural, three-tab, and slate-inspired asphalt</a>. Once you’ve selected the base style, you can choose from dozens of rich colors that are sure to enhance curb appeal.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durability</strong>: The Total Protection Roofing System® is a multi-layer roofing product that seals out weather and protects against damage. Moisture is kept out while still allowing for critical ventilation—resulting in a healthy, long-lasting roof.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Protection</strong>: On select Owens Corning roofing, you can opt for Class 4 roof shingles, which are rated for greater impact resistance from hail and wind. If you live in a severe weather area, these shingles can help prevent storm damage and may qualify for insurance discounts.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Longevity</strong>: Owens Corning roof systems are available with extended warranties that last up to 50 years, ensuring long-term performance for your home. Whether you need a <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">roof storm restoration</a> or a planned upgrade, this brand is an excellent choice.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3310, 292, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(3311, 292, 'left_content_header_3', 'Your Certified Roofing Contractor for Owens Corning'),
(3312, 292, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
(3313, 292, 'left_content_3', 'If you’re considering an Owens Corning roof, it’s critical to hire a qualified team of installers. Only certified roofers have gone through the requisite training and are able to offer premium warranty protections—and Bartlett Roofing is Owens Corning Preferred!\r\n\r\nIn addition to this manufacturer certification, we’re proud to maintain several other markers of excellence for both residential and <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing projects</a>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>BBB A+ Rating and Accreditation</li>\r\n 	<li>25+ Years of Industry Experience</li>\r\n 	<li>Large, Diverse Team of Trained Roof Installers</li>\r\n 	<li>Excellent Customer Reviews on Facebook and Google</li>\r\n 	<li>Inc. 5000 Honoree</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEven better?\r\n\r\nAbove and beyond the Owens Corning warranties that we’re able to offer, we back every new roofing system with our own 100% five-year workmanship warranty. We want you to be fully satisfied, and that\'s a promise we stand behind on every job.'),
