(3367, 293, 'left_content_1', 'Are you considering a new look for your roof system? Asphalt shingles may be the way to go. For the past 25+ years, the experts at Bartlett Roofing have been completing asphalt roof replacement projects of all sizes and scopes.\r\n\r\nWhen you work with our team, you can enjoy the best products from brands you can trust like <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\">Owens Corning</a>, GAF, IKO, and CertainTeed. That means you can rely on us to provide the best fit for your home exterior.'),
