(3369, 293, 'left_content_header_2', 'Top-Quality Asphalt Roofing Systems'),
(3370, 293, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(3371, 293, 'left_content_2', 'Asphalt roofing shingles are one of the most popular options for residential roof systems, especially when the installation is done by a professional roofing company. At Bartlett Roofing, we offer the best asphalt roof options for all types of homes. There are many reasons why you should choose an asphalt roof system for your home. For starters, asphalt systems are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Versatile</strong>: Asphalt shingles can cover all types of roof systems, regardless of size, shape, or roofline. Plus, we offer a wide range of designs, colors, and styles, so you can enhance your home’s curb appeal according to your personal aesthetic.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Cost-Effective</strong>: Asphalt roof shingles are one of the most affordable roofing options on the market. Not only are they cheaper to install, but they also last long enough to provide great value.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durable</strong>: Our roof shingles can withstand high winds, storms, and even fire in some cases. They’re also algae-resistant, so you don’t have to struggle with time-consuming maintenance.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low-Maintenance</strong>: An asphalt roof replacement with our roofing company is simple and stress-free. These shingles are easy to install, <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/repair/\">repair</a>, and maintain over time, which means you can enjoy the benefits of a quality roof system without a lot of hard work.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3372, 293, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(3373, 293, 'left_content_header_3', 'Schedule a Complimentary Inspection with Our Roofing Experts Today'),
(3374, 293, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
(3375, 293, 'left_content_3', 'As your <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing\">trusted roofing team</a>, Bartlett Roofing knows what it takes to find the perfect fit for your taste and your budget. We’ll be by your side from start to finish to ensure you get the best asphalt roof shingles for your property.\r\n\r\nAs an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, GAF-certified business, and CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator, we know what it takes to make your roofing project a breeze. In addition to our asphalt roof installation services, we provide a wide variety of materials for our roof <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement/\">replacement projects</a>. These include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Wood Shake</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile</li>\r\n 	<li>Slate</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal</li>\r\n 	<li>Low-Slope</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAre you ready to start planning your roof replacement project? Call our local roofing company to discuss your wants and needs with a professional or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection today.'),
