(3559, 296, 'left_content_1', 'Are you getting ready to replace your current roof? You’ve come to the right place. For the past 25+ years, our experts at Bartlett Roofing have been working with homeowners to enhance their roof systems.\r\n\r\nOver that time, our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement\">roof installation experts</a> have become Owens Corning Preferred Contractors, CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicators, GAF-certified roofers, and a BBB-accredited team. That means you can count on us to provide the best products for your roofing project. This promise extends to our slate roofing options, which is what we’re here to talk about.'),
