(3621, 297, 'left_content_1', 'Are you getting ready to replace your roof? Our experts at Bartlett Roofing are here to help. When <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement/\">replacing a roof system</a>, you’ll have to decide on the best material in terms of the appearance and performance you have in mind. At Bartlett Roofing, we offer a wide range of options from top brands, including Owens Corning, GAF, IKO, and CertainTeed.'),
