(3623, 297, 'left_content_header_2', 'Your Trusted Source Top-Rated Commercial Roof Repairs'),
(3624, 297, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(3625, 297, 'left_content_2', 'Bartlett Roofing is a professional metal roofing company, which means we offer the best products from trusted brands, so you can have peace of mind knowing you’re getting the highest-quality care for your roof system. Some of the top benefits of metal roofs specifically include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: Enjoy lower energy bills and a more comfortable interior. Our metal roofs are designed to reflect the sun’s UV rays instead of absorbing them.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durability</strong>: Our metal roof installers work hard to ensure our metal roofs stand strong against the elements, including high wind speeds.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Safety</strong>: Residential metal roofing is fire-resistant, so you don’t have to worry about lightning or similar hazards that can lead to a house fire.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendliness</strong>: Our metal roof options are often made from recycled materials and can be recycled yet again when the time comes for replacement.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Longevity</strong>: Most metal roof systems last between 40 and 70 years, though some are known to last upwards of 100 years! They also don’t require much in the way of maintenance or <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/repair/\">repairs</a> over time.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3626, 297, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(3627, 297, 'left_content_header_3', 'Learn More About Our Comprehensive Commercial Roofing Care Today'),
(3628, 297, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
(3629, 297, 'left_content_3', 'When it comes to keeping your roof system in top shape, there’s no one better to have on your side than the local metal roofers at Bartlett Roofing. With over two and a half decades of experience under our belt, we know what it takes to keep your home in peak condition through every season. Give us a call to learn about all our residential roofing offerings:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Professional Roof Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li>Home Roof Replacements</li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Low-Slope Roofs</li>\r\n 	<li>Wood Shake Options</li>\r\n 	<li>Slate Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li><em>… and more!</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDon’t leave your roof replacement project in just anyone’s hands. Get in touch with the <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing\">local roofing experts</a> at Bartlett Roofing to start planning your project with a complimentary inspection.'),
