(3685, 298, 'left_content_1', 'Searching for a professional flat roofing company? You’ve come to the right place. For the past 25+ years, Bartlett Roofing has been providing high-quality commercial roofing services for business owners across all industries.\r\n\r\nAlong the way, we have become an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified business, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator. We’re also a BBB-accredited business with an A+ rating. All this being said, you can count on us to make your roof renovations a breeze.'),
(3686, 298, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dae8178fa3'),
(3687, 298, 'left_content_header_2', 'Quality Low-Slope Options from Our Flat Roofers'),
(3688, 298, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dae9578fa4'),
(3689, 298, 'left_content_2', 'Bartlett Roofing is home to some of the top flat roofers that know how to design and install the highest-quality roof systems for properties throughout multiple states. So, what makes flat roofs so great anyway? Here are some of the top benefits:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Improved Heating and Cooling</strong>: A low-slope roof means a smaller attic, and that means there will be less space for air to get trapped. All that means lower energy bills!</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low-Maintenance Upkeep</strong>: Maintenance and repairs are much easier on flat roofs since they are safer and easier to access.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy and Affordable Installations</strong>: Low-slope roofs require fewer materials and easier to install overall, meaning your project will be that much more affordable.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Solar Compatibility</strong>: If you’re considering switching to solar in the near future, a flat roof system will be perfect. They are compatible with the latest solar technology.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Modern Style</strong>: Low-slope roofs offer a modern and contemporary aesthetic for your home or business. Our designers will help you create the perfect look for your space.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3690, 298, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dae9a78fa5'),
(3691, 298, 'left_content_header_3', 'Schedule a Complimentary Roof Inspection with Our Roofers Right Away'),
(3692, 298, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dae9f78fa6'),
(3693, 298, 'left_content_3', 'When you choose Bartlett Roofing as your <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing\">local roofing experts</a>, you can enjoy the ultimate peace of mind knowing you’re working with trained and certified professionals that care about your wants and needs for your roof system. In fact, our experts can handle a wide range of projects, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">Commercial Roofing</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you’re ready to start planning your project, give us a call or fill out our online form to receive a complimentary inspection today.'),
