(3749, 299, 'left_content_1', 'Bartlett Roofing is a professional roofing company, powered by a team with over 25 years of roofing experience. From the time we opened our doors until now, our team has earned an A+ rating and accreditation with the Better Business Bureau as well as certifications from Owens Corning, GAF, and CertainTeed.\r\n\r\nFrom <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">minor repairs</a> to full-scale replacements, we can handle all your roofing needs for your property. Here, we’ll specifically be talking about the latter: custom roof replacements.'),
(3750, 299, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(3751, 299, 'left_content_header_2', 'Comprehensive Commercial Roofing Options for Your Local Business'),
(3752, 299, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(3753, 299, 'left_content_2', 'As one of the top roof replacement companies, Bartlett Roofing knows what it takes to provide the best care for all types of businesses. When you work with our local experts, you can enjoy a host of benefits, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>No-Obligation Inspection</strong>: To start things off, we’ll come out to inspect your property and provide an accurate roof replacement estimate. That way, you know exactly what to expect and how to budget for your project.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Custom Roof Styles</strong>: We don’t settle for a “one-size-fits-all” solution. Instead, we offer a wide range of options, including <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/roof-coatings/\">roof coatings</a>, asphalt shingles, metal roofing, TPO roofs, and roof tiles.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Top-Quality Products</strong>: When you work with Bartlett Roofing, you can enjoy the best roofing products from brands you know you can trust, including Owens Corning, GAF, IKO, and CertainTeed.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Expert Installations</strong>: Our roofers are GAF-certified, Owens Corning Preferred Contractors, and CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicators. That means you can count on us to make your complete roof replacement a breeze.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3754, 299, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(3755, 299, 'left_content_header_3', 'Call Today to Learn More About Our Commercial Roof Replacement Options'),
(3756, 299, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_63192f9e025f1'),
(3757, 299, 'left_content_3', 'If you’re ready to learn more about our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing services</a>, get in touch with the local experts at Bartlett Roofing right away. Our team will be by your side through every step of the process to ensure you’re left with a durable roof system that lasts. Plus, we offer a wide range of products and services:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roof Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/multi-family-roofing/\">Multi-Family Roof Care</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Long-Lasting Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Asphalt Shingles</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roof Membranes</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing Options</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGet in touch with our local roofing team today to learn more about our roof replacement services. You can also fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection with our experts.'),
