(3867, 301, 'left_content_header_1', 'Multi-Family Roofing Contractors'),
(3868, 301, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_630dbc2c9a09e'),
(3869, 301, 'left_content_1', 'When it comes to multi-family home roofing projects, there’s no better partner to have by your side than Bartlett Roofing. Our professional commercial roofing company has over 25 years of experience designing and installing multi-family roofs for many different buildings.\r\n\r\nOn top of being a BBB-accredited business with an A+ rating, Bartlett Roofing is also GAF-certified, which means you can count on us to provide the best services for all our unique customers. Ready to learn more? Call the best multi-family roofing company near you right away!'),
(3870, 301, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(3871, 301, 'left_content_header_2', 'Enhance Your Properties with the Multi-Family Commercial Roofing Care'),
(3872, 301, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(3873, 301, 'left_content_2', 'At Bartlett Roofing, our goal is to make your multi-family home roofing project a breeze from beginning to end. We understand that you have a lot on your plate as a property owner, which is why we’ll be there to ease you through every step of the process. Some of our multi-family commercial roofing services and benefits include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Roof Inspections</strong>: We pride ourselves on not being pushy with potential customers, which is why we offer a complimentary consultation before you even agree to work with us! To top it off, we’ll provide an accurate estimate, too.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Comprehensive Services</strong>: Our multi-family roofers have experience working on a variety of different types of buildings, including apartments, townhomes, condos, and more. No matter what type of properties you own, we’ve got you covered.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Custom Roofing Options</strong>: We offer many different commercial roofing options and materials such as roof coatings, <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/tpo/\">TPO roofs</a>, metal, asphalt, and tile. We’ll also help you select the right colors and other details to ensure you get the best look for your multi-family roofs.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3874, 301, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(3875, 301, 'left_content_header_3', 'Call Our Commercial Roofers to Schedule a Complimentary Inspection'),
(3876, 301, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_63192f9e025f1'),
(3877, 301, 'left_content_3', 'As your trusted <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing team</a>, Bartlett Roofing will be by your side through every step of your roofing project to ensure you get the best care for your property. If you’re ready to start planning your project, you’re in the right place. You can also get in touch with our experts to learn more about our commercial roofing options:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Roof Replacements</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">Roof Repairs</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Roofing Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roofs</li>\r\n 	<li>Tile Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roof Options</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn the meantime, feel free to call us to chat with a team member about your multi-family roofing needs, or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection with our experts.'),
