(3928, 302, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_630dbc2c9a09e'),
(3929, 302, 'left_content_1', 'When it comes to <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/replacement/\">replacing your roof system</a>, there are many options from which you can choose. If you’re considering roof coatings, you’re in the right place. Bartlett Roofing has over 25 years of experience sourcing and installing top-quality roof coatings for properties of all shapes and sizes.\r\n\r\nAlong the way, we have become an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified business, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator. We’re also BBB-accredited with an A+ rating! All this being said, you can count on us to make your commercial roof coating project a breeze.'),
(3930, 302, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(3931, 302, 'left_content_header_2', 'Your Choice of Durable and Attractive Roof Coatings'),
(3932, 302, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(3933, 302, 'left_content_2', 'So, why should you consider roof coatings for your property anyway? To put it simply, they improve the performance of your roof and will increase its lifespan, too. They can either be sprayed or rolled onto the roof’s surface to protect the building from leaks and water damage.\r\n\r\nAs a single protective membrane, roof coatings don’t have seams, fasteners, or flashing capabilities. Here are some of the top benefits of flat roof coatings:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Water Protection</strong>: Since roof coatings consist of a single, seamless membrane, any form of water will be almost completely blocked from ruining your roof system and causing leaks. Even on the off-chance that a leak develops, it will be much easier to fix.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: Our commercial roofing coatings are reflective, meaning they bounce UV rays off your building instead of absorbing them. This will keep your space cooler overall, meaning you’ll have lower energy bills and happier employees!</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Easy Installations</strong>: A roof coating is very easy to install, whether you choose to have it sprayed on or rolled on. This means installing roof coatings will typically be less expensive than other roofing types.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(3934, 302, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(3935, 302, 'left_content_header_3', 'Get in Touch with Our Commercial Roofers to Start Planning Your Renovations Today'),
(3936, 302, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_63192f9e025f1'),
(3937, 302, 'left_content_3', 'When you choose Bartlett Roofing as your <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing team</a>, you can enjoy the best care from local roofers that understand your wants and needs for your property. In addition to our roof coating installations, our experts can also handle…\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">Roof Repairs and Maintenance</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Custom Roof Replacements</li>\r\n 	<li>Multi-Family Roofing Care</li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roof Shingle Installs</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roof System Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roofing Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof Tile Installs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAre you ready to explore our roof coating options for your property? Get in touch with our team to chat with a professional and get a complimentary inspection from our experts today.'),
