(3987, 303, 'left_content_1', 'Your commercial property is one of your most important investments, so when it’s time for a new roof, be sure that you choose a roofing company that delivers flawless results using premium asphalt roof replacement materials. By doing exactly that, the Bartlett Roofing team has built a solid reputation for excellence one job at a time.\r\n\r\nOur commitment to quality has earned us a long-standing A+ rating with the BBB, many positive customer reviews, and our place as the trusted choice for commercial roofing replacements and repairs.\r\n\r\nNo project is too big or too small, and we work to complete projects quickly to minimize disruption to your business’ normal routine.'),
