(4104, 305, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_630dbc2c9a09e'),
(4105, 305, 'left_content_1', 'As a business owner, you know how important it is to have a safe and durable property. Part of that means having a quality roof system. At Bartlett Roofing, we know what it takes to design and install the best roofs for all types of businesses, including high-quality TPO roofing.\r\n\r\nAs a BBB-accredited and A+ rated business, we can provide the best products, resources, and services to ensure you get the best fit for your space. Read on to learn more about our TPO roofing options.'),
(4106, 305, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(4107, 305, 'left_content_header_2', 'Your Trusted Source Top-Rated Commercial Roof Repairs'),
(4108, 305, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(4109, 305, 'left_content_2', 'TPO, or thermoplastic polyolefin, is designed mostly for low-slope roofs, but this flexible, versatile, and cost-effective material can be used on sloped roofs, too. When you choose to work with our local TPO roofers, you can enjoy the top TPO commercial roofing services for your property.\r\n\r\nSo, why choose TPO when you <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/replacement/\">replace your roof system</a>? For starters, TPO commercial roofing systems are:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficient</strong>: Our TPO roofing systems reflect solar heat instead of absorbing it, which will help lower your monthly energy bills.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendly</strong>: As far as commercial roofing options go, TPO is much easier on the environment because it can be recycled along with other plastics.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Durable</strong>: Our TPO roofs are resistant to fires, UV rays, many chemicals, and the elements, making them a great option for any type of business facility. TPO is also resistant to mold, dirt, impacts, and punctures.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Affordable</strong>: When compared to many other roofing materials like PVC and EPDM, TPO is a cost-effective option that lasts a long time, too.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Attractive</strong>: TPO is applied as a seamless membrane, which doesn’t only make it waterproof, but also provides a modern aesthetic for your building.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4110, 305, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
