(4165, 306, 'left_content_1', 'Planning a commercial roofing project can feel overwhelming, but it doesn’t have to be that way. Luckily, you have Bartlett Roofing to on your side to make the entire process a breeze.\r\n\r\nWith 25 years of experience and counting, our team uses the top roofing products from Owens Corning, CertainTeed, GAF, and IKO to protect and beautify local properties. We offer a wide range of roofing options for businesses of every size, and across all industries. Among our most popular options are our tile <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/replacement/\">roof replacement</a> systems.'),
(4166, 306, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dbc2c9da3d'),
(4167, 306, 'left_content_header_2', 'Your Choice of Quality Tile Roof Types'),
(4168, 306, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_63192f81c6103'),
(4169, 306, 'left_content_2', 'Having a high-quality roof system for your business will keep your employees and assets safe and secure. At Bartlett Roofing, we offer the best clay and concrete roof tiles that look great and last a lifetime. As a GAF-certified business, you can depend on us to provide the best installation care and customer support.\r\n\r\nSo, why choose a tile roof system anyways? The benefits are endless, but we’ll start here:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>High Resistance</strong>: Tile roof systems are highly resistant to both weather and pests, which means you won’t have to worry about expensive damage over time.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Low Maintenance</strong>: Because tile roofs are so durable, they require very little maintenance, saving you time and money on upkeep and repairs.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Impressive Longevity</strong>: Once you install a tile roof system, you can expect to have it for upwards of 50 years!</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Energy Efficiency</strong>: Purposely installed to leave a gap underneath, a tile roofing system will help block the sun’s heat, saving you money on energy bills from season to season.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Customizability</strong>: Our tile roof types come in a wide range of styles and colors, so you can completely customize your building’s exterior.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Eco-Friendliness</strong>: Since tiles are usually made from clay or concrete, they are completely sustainable and easily recyclable to lessen their impact on the environment.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4170, 306, '_left_content_2', 'field_63193032352d4'),
(4171, 306, 'left_content_header_3', 'Get in Touch with Our Commercial Roofers to Get a Complimentary Inspection Today'),
(4172, 306, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_63192f9e025f1'),
(4173, 306, 'left_content_3', 'When you choose Bartlett Roofing for your commercial roofing project, you can enjoy top-rated care from a local tile roof company with over two decades of experience under our belt. Our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing\">commercial roofers</a> will be by your side from start to finish with specialized care, affordable options, and protective warranties, too.\r\n\r\nIf you’re not sure where to start, get in touch with our team to learn about all our commercial roofing services:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Multi-Family Roofing Care</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Asphalt Roof Shingles</li>\r\n 	<li>Metal Roofing Options</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roof Systems</li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/repair/\">Roof Repairs</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Roof Replacements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you want a complimentary inspection for your upcoming project, fill out our simple online form or give us a call!'),
