(4277, 308, 'left_content_1', 'Roofing renovations aren’t always planned. If you should suddenly find yourself dealing with roof damage, our experts at Bartlett Roofing will be there to help with quick and effective storm restoration services. Over the past 25+ years, we have been perfecting <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/our-process/\">our process</a> to ensure our customers get the best care for their properties after a bad storm.\r\n\r\nAs a GAF-certified company, Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, and CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator, we know what it takes to keep your property in top shape no matter what.'),
(4278, 308, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dfc9190733'),
(4279, 308, 'left_content_header_2', 'Enjoy Comprehensive Storm Damage Repairs for Your Property'),
(4280, 308, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dfc91941ce'),
(4281, 308, 'left_content_2', 'When you choose Bartlett Roofing as your trusted storm restoration team, you can have peace of mind knowing you’re getting comprehensive care that meets your needs for your property. We’re regarded as one of the top local storm damage repair companies, so you can count on us to get the job done. Some of our services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Complimentary Inspection</strong>: First, our storm restoration contractors will come to your property to assess and document the damage sustained. We’ll also provide an accurate estimate, so you know what to expect.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Insurance Claims Assistance</strong>: On top of taking care of the actual damages, our team will help you file an <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/insurance-claims/\">insurance claim</a>. That way, you can get the best value from your storm damage repair project.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Water Damage Restoration</strong>: As a part of our storm restoration services, our team can fix water damage on many different types of roof systems, including asphalt, wood shake, tile, and more.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Roof Leak Repairs</strong>: Where water damage exists, leaks are sure to follow, which can be detrimental to your home. Our storm damage repair contractors will find the source of the leak and fix it, so you don’t have to worry about costly repair bills.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4282, 308, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dfc9197c52'),
(4283, 308, 'left_content_header_3', 'Get in Touch with Our Storm Restoration Experts to Get a Complimentary Inspection'),
(4284, 308, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dfc919b6c3'),
(4285, 308, 'left_content_3', 'If you’re in need of immediate care for your roof system, get in touch with our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration\">local storm restoration team</a> at Bartlett Roofing. We’ll be by your side from start to finish to ensure you get the best care for your property after a bad storm. In fact, we offer a wide range of storm damage restoration services, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/hail-damage/\">Hail Damage Restoration</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/wind-damage/\">Wind Damage Repairs</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Insurance Claims Work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGive us a call to chat with a professional or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection with our local restoration and roofing company today.'),
