(4336, 309, 'left_content_2', 'As a local roofing company, Bartlett Roofing knows what it takes to shield your home from the climate all year long. Through our wind restoration services, we’ll be able to restore your property to its pre-storm condition without a hitch. In fact, we pride ourselves on our seamless <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/our-process/\">restoration process</a>. Here’s what you can expect when you work with our storm repair contractors:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Wind Damage Repairs</strong>: High winds can cause many problems for your roof system, including peeling and curling shingles, soffits and fascia damage, missing shingles, and granule loss. Whatever the extent of the damage, you can count on our experts to fix everything with ease.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Full Roof Restoration</strong>: If the damage your roof has sustained is too severe, we’ll be able to completely replace your roof system. We offer the best roofing products from CertainTeed, GAF, Owens Corning, and IKO that come in a variety of styles and materials. That way, you can get the best look for your home at a price that suits your budget.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Insurance Claims Care</strong>: On top of everything else, our wind restoration company also has the top <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/insurance-claims/\">insurance specialists</a> on our side. We can handle everything from documenting the damage and filing reports to meeting with your insurance adjusters and ensuring you get the most value out of your restoration project.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4337, 309, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dfc9197c52'),
