(4340, 309, 'left_content_3', 'Keeping your property safe has never been easier than with the trusted experts at Bartlett Roofing on your side. Our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm damage restoration team</a> has over 25 years of experience under our belt handling the worst damage, so we guarantee the best care no matter the circumstances. As a full-service storm damage restoration company, we offer:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Hail Damage Restoration</li>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing Care</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Roof Repairs and Maintenance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you’re in need of immediate service, give us a call to talk to a team member today. Otherwise, you can fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection.'),
