(4526, 313, 'left_content_1', 'Roofing renovations aren’t always planned. If you should suddenly find yourself dealing with roof damage, our experts at Bartlett Roofing will be there to help with quick and effective storm restoration services. Over the past 25+ years, we have been perfecting <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/our-process/\">our process</a> to ensure our customers get the best care for their properties after a bad storm.\r\n\r\nAs a GAF-certified company, Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, and CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator, we know what it takes to keep your property in top shape no matter what.'),
(4527, 313, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dfc9190733'),
