(4534, 313, 'left_content_3', 'If you’re in need of immediate care for your roof system, get in touch with our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration\">local storm restoration team</a> at Bartlett Roofing. We’ll be by your side from start to finish to ensure you get the best care for your property after a bad storm. In fact, we offer a wide range of storm damage restoration services, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/hail-damage/\">Hail Damage Restoration</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/wind-damage/\">Wind Damage Repairs</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Insurance Claims Work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nGive us a call to chat with a professional or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection with our local restoration and roofing company today.'),
