(4652, 316, 'left_content_1', 'If you have questions about roof insurance claims, you aren’t alone! Each year, Bartlett Roofing works with hundreds of homeowners and their families to navigate the <a href=\"https://bartlettroofscom.azurewebsites.net/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm damage roof</a> claim process. If you choose to work with our insurance roof replacement experts, you’ll have a certified team by your side to guide you through the insurance process and help you get the coverage needed to fix your roof damage.\r\n\r\nWe bring more than 25 years of proven experience and are proud to be:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>BBB A+ Rated and Accredited</li>\r\n 	<li>Owens Corning Preferred Contractors</li>\r\n 	<li>CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicators</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF Certified Roofers</li>\r\n 	<li>Inc. 5000 Honorees</li>\r\n</ul>'),
