(4710, 317, 'left_content_1', 'Bartlett Roofing started out as a family-owned framing crew back in the early 90s. Today, owner Doug Bartlett has transformed the business into a full-service roofing and restoration business that services multiple states throughout the country, including Idaho, Montana, Nevada, Oregon, Utah, Washington, and Wyoming. Our top-rated services now include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Solutions</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Damage Restoration Care</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(4711, 317, '_left_content_1', 'field_630dfcbdd9fc2'),
(4712, 317, 'left_content_header_2', 'The Bartlett Method'),
(4713, 317, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_630dfcbddd9c4'),
(4714, 317, 'left_content_2', 'Doug Bartlett learned everything he knows about the exterior remodeling industry from his dad and uncle. Through the years, Doug has built the Bartlett Roofing team from the ground up, training and educating them in the Bartlett Method.\r\n\r\nThe staple of the Bartlett Method is to provide comprehensive care that meets our customers’ unique wants and needs. When the project is over, we want to be able to ask our clients if they are 100% satisfied and have them come back with a guaranteed “yes!”'),
(4715, 317, '_left_content_2', 'field_630dfcbde1491'),
(4716, 317, 'left_content_header_3', 'What Our Roofing and Restoration Specialists Have to Offer'),
(4717, 317, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_630dfcbde4fc8'),
(4718, 317, 'left_content_3', 'Bartlett Roofing cares about all our customers. For us, this is more than a job; it’s an opportunity to better local communities throughout these western states. Furthermore, we’re a BBB-accredited and A+ rated business, so we have the skills and resources to make any project a breeze. Some of our amazing benefits include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Complimentary Roof Inspections and Project Estimates</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF-Certified Roofing and Restoration Experts</li>\r\n 	<li>Custom Roof Materials from Top-Rated Brands</li>\r\n 	<li>Efficient Roof Repairs and Maintenance Plans</li>\r\n 	<li>Workmanship Coverage from Day of Completion</li>\r\n 	<li>Protective Owens Corning Warranties</li>\r\n 	<li>Affordable Prices and Flexible Financing Options</li>\r\n 	<li><em>… and so much more!</em></li>\r\n</ul>'),
