(4789, 323, 'left_content_1', '<div class=\"offer-hero\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://cmsplatform.blob.core.windows.net/wwwbartlettroofscom/offers/images/large/355b1897-0811-473a-b697-01fd19b3a72d.png\" alt=\"Quick Apply Now: One-Step Financing Applications!\" /></div>\r\nGetting your roof replaced is a big, expensive project that many homeowners only take on when they absolutely have to do so. It can be a challenge to pay for your new roof, especially when you have to replace it suddenly.\r\n\r\nAt Bartlett Roofing, we strive to make the <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement/\" rel=\"nofollow\">roof replacement process</a> as easy and affordable as possible for our customers. We’re able to offer financing options through companies like Hearth and EnerBank that allow homeowners to get much-needed roofing work done.'),
(4790, 323, '_left_content_1', 'field_631811a24a764'),
(4791, 323, 'left_content_header_2', 'Easy Payment Plan Application Process'),
(4792, 323, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_631811a24e2fa'),
(4793, 323, 'left_content_2', 'If you are interested in applying for a financing plan that will help you to install a roof or to complete roof repairs, just let us know. We offer a <strong>hassle-free quick-apply option</strong>—taking just one step to complete!\r\n\r\nYou can contact Bartlett Roofing to get more information about our financing plans and start the application process. You can also let our professionals know during the roofing inspection that you’ll want to apply for financing.'),
(4794, 323, '_left_content_2', 'field_631811a251dac'),
(4795, 323, 'left_content_header_3', 'Learn More About Our Roofing Services'),
(4796, 323, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_631811a255856'),
(4797, 323, 'left_content_3', 'It’s not hard to see the benefits of breaking up your roofing costs into monthly payments with a financing plan. Plus, this option is available with most of <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">our roofing services</a>, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you are thinking about replacing your roof in any of the states we serve, consider reaching out to Bartlett Roofing today. Our BBB-accredited and A+ rated team can set up a complimentary 40-Point Roof Inspection to assess the condition of your property. If you need <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/repair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">roof repairs</a>, we’ll create a complimentary quote right away. Our team can also go over the financing options available with you.\r\n\r\nGive us a call to set up your roofing inspection right away, or fill out our online form to request more information about a financing plan.'),
