(4885, 320, 'left_content_2', 'Roof renovations and maintenance are some of the most important exterior projects to stay on top of as a property owner. Whether you need work done on your home or business property, our local roofing experts at Bartlett Roofing will be there to help. Explore our services and get in touch with our roofers to start planning:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/\">Residential Roofing</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">Commercial Roofing</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">Storm Damage Restoration</a></li>\r\n</ul>'),
