(5017, 351, 'left_content_1', 'When it comes to keeping your property’s exterior in top shape, it’s important to have a local team on your side that you can trust. Luckily, you found us! Bartlett Roofing is a professional roofing and storm restoration company with over 25 years of experience under our belt working with homeowners and business owners alike.\r\n\r\nMoreover, we’re an A+ rated, BBB-accredited business, an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified business, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator. That said, we know what we’re doing when it comes to roofing projects!'),
