(5067, 352, 'left_content_1', '<div class=\"offer-hero\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://cmsplatform.blob.core.windows.net/wwwbartlettroofscom/offers/images/large/6b0e9ace-a903-4d69-b6ee-8a1042b16b07.png\" alt=\"Get 100% Warranty Coverage on Labor for 5 Years!\" /></div>\r\nYou may be wondering what makes Bartlett Roofing different from other nationwide roofing companies. We put every effort into providing for the customer’s needs before, during, and after <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/replacement/\" rel=\"nofollow\">roof replacement projects</a>. Our team does exceptional work that will last for decades to come. But we also understand that homeowners want peace of mind with such a large investment in their properties.\r\n\r\nThat’s why we offer a <strong>100% workmanship warranty for 5 years</strong> from day one of project completion.\r\n\r\nYou’ll have the comfort of knowing our team will come out to fix any problems with your roof resulting from improper installation—at no cost to you. No need to pay for labor hours. No need to worry about unexpected fees.'),
(5068, 352, '_left_content_1', 'field_631811a24a764'),
(5069, 352, 'left_content_header_2', 'Get a Premier Manufacturer’s Warranty for Your Roof'),
(5070, 352, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_631811a24e2fa'),
(5071, 352, 'left_content_2', 'We’re also proud to be certified roofers for many of the brands we work with, like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Owens Corning</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF</li>\r\n 	<li>CertainTeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to proving our comprehensive factory training in their products, these certifications also allow us to extend extra warranty protections for your roof.\r\n\r\nYour <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Owens Corning roof</a> will automatically be covered by their prorated lifetime warranty, but with us you’ll also have the option of adding extended coverage. Owens Corning offers three levels of extended coverage that increase the length of the TRU PROtection period — from 10 years up to 50 years. You’ll also enjoy other additional benefits with these upgraded coverages.'),
