(5161, 355, 'left_content_2', 'We’re also proud to be certified roofers for many of the brands we work with, like:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Owens Corning</li>\r\n 	<li>GAF</li>\r\n 	<li>CertainTeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to proving our comprehensive factory training in their products, these certifications also allow us to extend extra warranty protections for your roof.\r\n\r\nYour <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/roofing/owens-corning/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Owens Corning roof</a> will automatically be covered by their prorated lifetime warranty, but with us you’ll also have the option of adding extended coverage. Owens Corning offers three levels of extended coverage that increase the length of the TRU PROtection period — from 10 years up to 50 years. You’ll also enjoy other additional benefits with these upgraded coverages.'),
(5162, 355, '_left_content_2', 'field_631811a251dac'),
(5163, 355, 'left_content_header_3', 'What is the TRU PROtection Period?'),
(5164, 355, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_631811a255856'),
(5165, 355, 'left_content_3', 'Just about every Owens Corning warranty covers both materials and the labor required to remove or repair defective products for a certain length of time. As you can imagine, the addition of labor protection can save you a lot of money.\r\n\r\nMost of their standard warranties will cover labor for 10 years. After that decade passes, your Owens Corning warranty will only cover the cost of materials. We can offer you extended warranties that provide labor and materials coverage for what is essentially the entire lifespan of the roof.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in learning more about our warranty coverages, fill out our online form to have a representative contact you. If you would like to get a complimentary roof inspection and estimate for any of the following, give Bartlett Roofing a call:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Commercial Roofing</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nLet Bartlett Roofing provide you with a beautiful new roof that is also protected by extensive warranties. We’ll make sure you don’t have to worry about replacement in the near or far future.'),
