(6085, 588, 'left_content_1', '<div>\r\n<div class=\"post-meta\">By <span class=\"post-author\"><a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/blog/a.bartlett-roofing/\">Bartlett Roofing</a> </span><time class=\"post-date text-muted\">August 19, 2022</time></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"post-body\">\r\n<p class=\"post-excerpt\">If you want to start a new career, you may be curious about the benefits of joining the roofing industry. Roofing is an in-demand trade that brings job satisfaction to thousands of roofers across the country. No matter what state you are in, you can find roofing opportunities that require your skill...</p>\r\n<a class=\"post-continue btn-page-link\" href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/blog/p.220819000/why-now-is-the-best-time-to-join-the-roofing-industry/\">Read More</a>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
