(8090, 793, 'left_content_1', 'Roofing and restoration projects come in all shapes and sizes, and our team at Bartlett Roofing can handle them all. Since we first opened our doors over 25 years ago, our BBB-accredited Boise roofing company has been repairing and replacing roof systems of all types for homeowners and businesses, too.\r\n\r\nPlus, we’ve put in the time and effort to become an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified business, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator. Whatever the project, we’ve got you covered with the best care revolving around:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Home Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Business Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Repairs</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(8091, 793, '_left_content_1', 'field_631a993f422e0'),
(8092, 793, 'left_content_header_2', 'Take Your Home’s Roof System to the Next Level with Our Boise Roofing Team'),
(8093, 793, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_631a993f45c5f'),
(8094, 793, 'left_content_2', 'Bartlett Roofing is also a <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">top-quality commercial roofing company</a> in Boise, which means you can count on us to provide the best services for your property. With our commercial roofing contractors on your side, you can enjoy comprehensive care, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Custom Roof Replacement Options</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li>New Roof Installation Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Strong Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Multi-Family Roof Services</li>\r\n 	<li><em>… and more!</em></li>\r\n</ul>'),
(8095, 793, '_left_content_2', 'field_631a993f50dc9'),
(8096, 793, 'left_content_header_3', 'Your Local Commercial Roofing Experts in Boise, ID'),
(8097, 793, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_631a993f4d282'),
