(8099, 793, '_left_content_header_4', 'field_631a993f5490d'),
(8100, 793, 'left_content_4', 'It’s no secret that you’re going to have to deal with tough storms when you live in Idaho. In fact, your property can sustain a lot of damage over time. That’s why it’s important to have a professional Boise <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm restoration and roofing company</a> ready to help you pick up the pieces. Our storm restoration services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Insurance claims filing</strong>, so you can get the best value out of your restoration project.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Wind damage</strong> repairs such as repairing curling or peeling shingles, replacing roof systems, and repairing damages from fallen debris.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hail damage restoration care</strong>, including roof replacements, repairs for pits and holes, and more.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Storm damage repairs </strong>such as water damage, leak repairs, full roof replacements, and anything in between.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(8101, 793, '_left_content_4', 'field_631a993f583c0'),
(8102, 793, 'left_content_header_5', 'Get in Touch with Our Roofing Experts in Boise to Get a Complimentary Consultation Today'),
