(8146, 661, 'left_content_4', 'Has a bad storm swept through the Upper Midwest? Your home’s roof may have suffered damage from wind or hail. Make sure to have it checked out by the <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">roof restoration experts</a> at Bartlett Roofing. We’ll go over the property with a keen eye for detail, checking for signs of damage such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Missing or Lifted Shingles</li>\r\n 	<li>Dings and Dents</li>\r\n 	<li>Warped or Damaged Flashing</li>\r\n 	<li>Water Leaks and Damage</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf needed, we can also help you decide whether roof restoration or replacement is the best way to proceed, so your property has the protection it needs for a lifetime.'),
