(9718, 667, 'left_content_header_1', 'Eagle, ID Roofing and Storm Restoration Contractors'),
(9719, 667, '_left_content_header_1', 'field_631a993f3e798'),
(9720, 667, 'left_content_1', 'As a property owner, you already know how important it is to keep your roof system in good condition. At Bartlett Roofing, we go above and beyond to ensure this vital home feature looks and performs at its best throughout the year. As a local Eagle roofing company, we know what it takes to handle repairs and roof replacement projects that meet the needs of all our local customers.\r\n\r\nBartlett Roofing is a BBB-accredited business with an A+ rating. Plus, we\'ve earned the approval of major manufacturers as an Owens Corning Preferred Contractor, a GAF-certified company, and a CertainTeed Master Shingle Applicator.\r\n\r\nThat means we can complete many projects with ease:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roof Care</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration Solutions</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(9721, 667, '_left_content_1', 'field_631a993f422e0'),
(9722, 667, 'left_content_header_2', 'Your Eagle Residential Roofing Experts'),
(9723, 667, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_631a993f45c5f'),
(9724, 667, 'left_content_2', 'On top of our home roofing care, Bartlett Roofing can handle a wide range of commercial roofing projects. Our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">commercial roofing contractors</a> have over 25 years of experience dealing with all types of renovations.\r\n\r\nAs one of the top commercial roofing companies in Eagle, we have the best products and services for all your roofing needs:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Roof Repair Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Replacement Roof Care</li>\r\n 	<li>Custom Roof Materials</li>\r\n 	<li>Multi-Family Roofing Options</li>\r\n 	<li>Top-Quality Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li><em>… and more!</em></li>\r\n</ul>'),
(9725, 667, '_left_content_2', 'field_631a993f49751'),
(9726, 667, 'left_content_header_3', 'Professional Commercial Roofing Services'),
(9727, 667, '_left_content_header_3', 'field_631a993f4d282'),
(9728, 667, 'left_content_header_4', 'Superior Storm Restoration Care in Eagle, ID'),
(9729, 667, '_left_content_header_4', 'field_631a993f5490d'),
(9730, 667, 'left_content_4', 'Living in Idaho, you’re no stranger to the demanding climate. As your trusted local Eagle roofing company, our <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm restoration contractors</a> at Bartlett Roofing know how to deal with all types of weather.\r\n\r\nNo matter what type of storm restoration services you need, you can count on us to get your property back in pre-storm condition in no time. Get in touch to learn more about our restoration care and insurance claims services, too.'),
(9731, 667, '_left_content_4', 'field_631a993f583c0'),
(9732, 667, 'left_content_header_5', 'Call Our Eagle Roofing and Restoration Team to Schedule a Complimentary Inspection'),
(9733, 667, '_left_content_header_5', 'field_631a9caeca2a7'),
(9734, 667, 'left_content_5', 'When you work with Bartlett Roofing, you get to enjoy professional care from local experts that care about your wants and needs for your property. If you’re ready to start planning your own roofing project, give us a call or fill out our online form to schedule a complimentary inspection and get an accurate estimate today.'),
