(9909, 671, '_left_content_header_4', 'field_631a993f5490d'),
(9910, 671, 'left_content_4', 'Storms are a frequent occurrence in Idaho, which is why it’s important to have a local <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/storm-damage-restoration/\">storm restoration and roofing company</a> on your side. As local Garden City storm restoration contractors, Bartlett Roofing understands what it takes to protect your property from the worst of the Idaho weather.\r\n\r\nFirst, we’ll come for a complimentary inspection, so you can get an idea of the scope of damage your roof system has sustained. After that, our storm restoration services will include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Wind Restoration</strong>: Replacing peeling, curling, or missing shingles, dealing with granule loss, repairing holes from fallen debris.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hail Restoration</strong>: Dealing with pits and holes in the roof system, repairing damaged shingles, restoring entire sections of roof.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Storm Restoration</strong>: Repairing water damage to roof system, stopping interior leaks, replacing roof systems.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Insurance Claims Care</strong>: Filing paperwork, meeting with insurance adjusters, and ensuring you get the most value out of your repairs.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
