(9947, 818, '_left_content_header_2', 'field_631a993f45c5f'),
(9948, 818, 'left_content_2', 'When it comes to keeping your business property in top shape, there’s no one better to have on your side than the <a href=\"https://www.bartlettroofs.com/commercial-roofing/\">professional commercial roofing contractors</a> at Bartlett Roofing. Our commercial roofing company knows how to deal with a wide range of projects for commercial properties of all shapes and sizes. Choose from the best commercial roofing materials and options, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Top-Rated Roof Coatings</li>\r\n 	<li>Flexible Asphalt Roof Options</li>\r\n 	<li>Eco-Friendly Metal Roofs</li>\r\n 	<li>TPO Roofing Options</li>\r\n 	<li>Attractive Tile Roof Systems</li>\r\n</ul>'),
