(10216, 677, 'left_content_1', 'In need of stellar roofing care? Bartlett Roofing is a professional roofing company in Kuna that is ready to tackle any and all residential and commercial roofing projects. Since we first opened our doors over two decades ago, our goal has been to improve the lives of our local customers through our hard work and top-quality products. With our roofing contractors on your side, you can enjoy comprehensive roofing and storm restoration services. Read on to learn more about our:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Residential Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Commercial Roofing</li>\r\n 	<li>Storm Restoration Care</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(10217, 677, '_left_content_1', 'field_631a993f422e0'),
